      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STAR TURN (1) has a strong overall record having 17 wins and 18 places from 49 starts including a last start third (25.53) over 457m at this track. Solid record here winning two races. Rates strongly and will go close from the inside draw. ARMARTA (7) was prominent throughout when winning two back then got further back last time but came home hard into second and beaten half a length at Q Straight (19.24). Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Leading player again. MR. LASSO (6) had been going along well winning a Grade 5 three back then placing at Rockhampton before missing the frame latest when sixth (29.92) at Rockhampton. Has the ability and expected to do much better. SUPER SCRUB (8) cannot be ruled out.",
